He is like a time bomb.

00:23:27.760 --> 00:23:28.520
No.

00:23:28.590 --> 00:23:30.590
I must push him to Chen Chuchu.

00:23:31.000 --> 00:23:32.590
When the story ends,

00:23:33.240 --> 00:23:34.400
I'll be able to go home.

