What is a screenplay?

00:23:50.520 --> 00:23:52.350
It's a story.

00:23:53.350 --> 00:23:54.800
A storyteller?

00:23:54.920 --> 00:23:56.350
Yes. That's it.

00:23:56.550 --> 00:23:58.470
How do I call a storyteller?

